item.title: Rousing Flow Touches The Sensual Side With Play Music
item.description:
Rousing Flow Touches The Sensual Side With Play Music

Arizona based Rousing Flow is an artist with a paintbrush full of frequencies which has created an engaging, beautiful soundscape of instrumental awesomeness. Play Music is a sensual experience packed into 13 compositions of grooving instrumentals driven by smooth rhythms and caressing melodies.

item.title: Rousing Flow - 'Play Music'
item.description:
Rousing Flow - 'Play Music'

Readers of the Independent Spotlight know that Garageband is my go-to when I refer to shoddy self-production, particularly in the hip-hop community. For all of the shots I fire at it, however, I do understand its potential. It's a remarkably good digital audio workstation for a beginner that has versatility unparalleled in comparative suites.

item.title: Indie Band GuruRousing Flow Gets the Instrumental Flow Going in "Play Music"
item.description:
Indie Band GuruRousing Flow Gets the Instrumental Flow Going in "Play Music"

Rousing Flow is maybe one of the most interesting artist names that I have heard thus far, mostly because of the authenticity of the name. I mean, what a way to describe your sound through putting it right there in your name (great publicity move).
